But in that case the driver must pay five hundred crowns.
Drivers who are required to change their license and do not reach until the end of the year, but will hit the roads without the valid card will risk a fine starting in January.
The offender will pay a maximum of two thousand crowns.
The police officer can arrange the infraction with a reprimand.
If it is an administrative offence, the fine shall be 2,500 kroner.
